Class Description
Bishop
The Bishop class extends to the Piece class and creates and manages a Bishop Piece.
Board
The Board class hosts all the pieces and Nodes where the game is played
Chess
The Chess class manages the Chess game between players
King
The Bishop class extends to the Piece class and creates and manages a King Piece.

The Knight class extends to the Piece class and creates and manages a Knight Piece.
